<div class="scene-titre-sans-variation">SCENE II.</div>
<p class="didascalie"><em><span class="variation" data-tooltip="1664, 1676: IOCASTE, ANTIGONE, OLYMPE.

">JOCASTE, ANTIGONE, OLYMPE. </span></em></p>
<div class="locuteur"><span style="font-variant: small-caps;"><span class="variation" style="font-variant: small-caps;" data-tooltip="1664, 1676: Iocaste.

">Jocaste. </span></span></div>
